### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = <paste_token_here>

### Signup
POST {{baseUrl}}/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "pankaj",
  "email": "pankaj@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "pankaj@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Get Current User (protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
